{{Nihongo|'''''Thermae Romae II'''''|テルマエ・ロマエＩＩ}} is a 2014 Japanese [[comedy film]] directed by [[Hideki Takeuchi]] and based on the [[manga]] series ''[[Thermae Romae]]'' by [[Mari Yamazaki]].<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.allcinema.net/prog/show_c.php?num_c=347375|script-title=ja:テルマエ・ロマエＩＩ (2014)|accessdate= 30 April 2014|work= allcinema.net|publisher= Stingray|language= Japanese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.tokyohive.com/article/2014/04/abe-hiroshi-ueto-aya-and-more-attend-thermae-romae-ii-premiere|title= Abe Hiroshi, Ueto Aya and more attend 'Thermae Romae II' Premiere|date= 27 April 2014|accessdate= 30 April 2014|work= tokyohive|publisher= 6Theory Media, LLC}}</ref>

==Cast==
*[[Hiroshi Abe (actor)|Hiroshi Abe]]
*[[Aya Ueto]]
*[[Kazuki Kitamura]]
*[[Takashi Sasano]]
*[[Anthony Ripoll]]

==Reception==
The film has grossed [[Yen|¥]]4.2 billion in Japan.<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-06-23/japanese-box-office-june-14-15/.75830|title=  Japanese Box Office, June 14-15|date= 23 June 2014|accessdate= 24 June 2014|work= [[Anime News Network]]}}</ref>

